# 🎯 Event Management Dashboard

A full-stack MERN application for managing events with secure admin login, event dashboard, registration system, and responsive UI.

---

## 📦 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React, Axios, Toastify
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js, JWT
- **Database**: MongoDB (via Mongoose)
- **Auth**: JSON Web Tokens (JWT)
- **Email**: Nodemailer (Gmail SMTP)

---

## ✅ Features

### 👤 Admin Authentication
- Secure login with JWT
- Forgot password (email link)
- Reset password functionality

### 📋 Event Management
- Add new event with details
- View all events in card layout
- Register user to event (seat count logic)
- Delete events

### 📊 Dashboard
- Total Events
- Total Registered Users
- Available Seats

### 💡 UI/UX
- Clean layout with `EventCard`, `EventForm`, `Dashboard`
- Responsive design
- Dark mode toggle
- Search filter by event title
- Toast notifications

---

